<DOC><DOCNO> WSJ870602-0144 </DOCNO><HL> Wyse Technology SlatesPurchase of California Firm</HL><DD> 06/02/87</DD><SO> WALL STREET JOURNAL (J)</SO><IN> WYSETENDER OFFERS, MERGERS, ACQUISITIONS (TNM) </IN><DATELINE> SAN JOSE, Calif.  </DATELINE><TEXT>   Wyse Technology said it agreed in principle to acquire Link Technologies Inc. for common stock. The amount wasn't disclosed.    The plan is subject to certain conditions, including the approval of Link's shareholders.    Wyse supplies video display products. Closely held Link Technologies, Fremont, Calif., develops and markets computer terminals. Link employs about 60 people, a Wyse spokesman said. </TEXT></DOC>